yle="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">✔️ No long term commitments. Our subscribers simply love The Lift Box and stay in the community.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><!--StartFragment--><!--EndFragment--></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">✔️<span>&nbsp;</span></strong>We send surveys 30 days after&nbsp;every&nbsp;box.&nbsp;If you take 2 minutes to fill them out, you'll receive a $5 off code EVERY time.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div><span class="gf_tab-accordion-title"><span></span></span><div data-index="2" data-key="content1" class="item-content gf_tab-panel"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" id="e-1622123474406" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1622123474406" data-resolution="960x960"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/a844e65b-da3d-4ebd-a170-06424f59ba80/-/format/auto/-/preview/960x960/-/quality/lighter/Untitleddesign_95_e62aee99-233e-47c5-a375-afbeeb39285b.png" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="auto" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="1200"></div></div></div><span class="gf_tab-accordion-title"><span></span></span><div data-index="3" data-key="content1" class="item-content gf_tab-panel"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1620335999041" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1620335999041"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">WHAT KIND OF ITEMS ARE INCLUDED IN THE LIFT BOX?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Every month, we partner with exciting brands to get you a different variety of supplements, snacks, and workout gear or equipment, as well as a shirt or tank in our custom fit styles and great designs. We take pride in only sending the best, high quality products and test everything out ourselves first. You can get sneak peeks monthly over on our socials and check out the monthly brands we featured on Headlines Over Sidelines.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">WHAT’S THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN THE WOMEN AND MEN’S LIFT BOX?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The only difference is between the shirt styles! All other products are identical. The Women’s shirt is a more fitted cut, with a scoop neck design. We recommend sizing up from your traditional street size, due to the athletic cut. The Men’s style is closer to the typical Unisex, however it is still an athletic cut. If you have any issues with the fit or style of your shirt, please reach out to us!</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">HOW DO I EDIT AND UPDATE SIZE INFORMATION?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">You are able to update any upcoming orders sizing directly in your profile. For any current processing orders, please reach out to us at info@theliftbx.com to change sizing. If you receive a shirt that just isn’t fitting the way you hoped, reach out to us and we will get you a new size!&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">CAN I GET MY BOX VEGAN/GLUTEN FREE/SUGAR FREE?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">At this time, we are unable to accommodate any customization for dietary needs. We do feature brands who are gluten free or vegan often but our brand partnership changes monthly. You can get sneak peeks of what we are featuring every month on our social media pages.&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">WHEN DOES MY BOX SHIP?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">We pack and ship out the boxes during the week of the 20th, every month. If you order prior to the 15th, you are guaranteed a spot during pack week. Any orders placed after the 15th are allocated to the following month unless we have yet to sell out of the current month. You will receive a shipping confirmation via email with tracking information.&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">WHEN DOES THE BOX RENEW?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Every month on the 1st at midnight. Any changes or cancellations made to the account after this date will apply to any FOLLOWING orders, not the current one. Please reach out to us if you need assistance with a current month’s order.&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">HOW DO I CANCEL?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Simply log into your account, click “Edit Subscriptions” and hit the “Cancel” button. You can cancel, or pause, any time without hassle. If you need assistance of any kind, please reach out to us via chat, email, or text at any time. We respond within 24 hours. Just a heads up, if you’ve already paid for this monthly, this will only cancel any future orders, not current ones.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div><span class="gf_tab-accordion-title"><span></span></span><div data-index="4" data-key="content1" class="item-content gf_tab-panel"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1622123426588" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1622123426588"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">Your first month's subscription will be charged when you checkout. After you receive your first box, all subscription accounts are charged on the 1st of every month.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">We ship our boxes out the week of the 20th every month and will send your box confirmation and tracking info via email.</p><p><!--StartFragment--></p><p style="margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.6em;"><br style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;"><!--EndFragment--></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_clearfix"></div></div></div></article></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" id="e-1686772276027" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1686772276027"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><strong style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">MAKING THE NEWS SINCE 2017</strong></h3></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" id="r-1686772275963" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-3" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1686772275963" data-extraclass="" data-row-gap="3px"><div class="gf_column gf