; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">✔️<span>&nbsp;</span></strong>We send surveys 30 days after&nbsp;every&nbsp;box.&nbsp;If you take 2 minutes to fill them out, you'll receive a $5 off code EVERY time.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div><span class="gf_tab-accordion-title"><span></span></span><div data-index="2" data-key="content1" class="item-content gf_tab-panel"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1640618808471" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1640618808471"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>*For women's t-shirts only, we recommend getting one size up.</p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" id="e-1640618808481" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1640618808481" data-resolution="960x960"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/a844e65b-da3d-4ebd-a170-06424f59ba80/-/format/auto/-/preview/960x960/-/quality/lighter/Untitleddesign_95_e62aee99-233e-47c5-a375-afbeeb39285b.png" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="auto" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="1200"></div></div></div><span class="gf_tab-accordion-title"><span></span></span><div data-index="3" data-key="content1" class="item-content gf_tab-panel"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1640618808470" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1640618808470"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">WHAT KIND OF ITEMS ARE INCLUDED IN THE BOX?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Every month you’ll get a different mix of products like workout apparel, supplements, gear, equipment, and other surprises to keep you motivated. All products that are chosen have been tested by The Lift Box team and only the best make it to you. We take great pride to send only the best, high quality products and focus on bringing you new brands you've never tried before.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">WHEN DOES MY BOX SHIP?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Each month boxes ship out the week of the 20th and tracking info is sent via email.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">HOW DO I CANCEL?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Simply log into your account, click edit subscription and hit the cancel button. Cancel anytime without the hassle, and if you need assistance, we are always available to help via email, text, or live chat.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">CAN I EDIT AND UPDATE SIZE INFORMATION?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Reach out to us at info@theliftbx.com for help whenever you need it but you always have control to log in to your account to update your size and info yourself too.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><!--StartFragment--><!--EndFragment--><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">DO YOU SHIP INTERNATIONALLY?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><!--StartFragment--><!--EndFragment--></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Not yet, but we're working on it. We do ship to overseas military bases though!</p></div></div></div><span class="gf_tab-accordion-title"><span></span></span><div data-index="4" data-key="content1" class="item-content gf_tab-panel"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1640618808425" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1640618808425"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">Your first month's subscription will be charged when you checkout. After that, all subscription accounts are charged on the 1st of every month.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">We ship our boxes out the week of the 20th every month and will send your box confirmation and tracking info via email.</p><p><!--StartFragment--></p><p style="margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.6em;"><br style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;"><!--EndFragment--></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_clearfix"></div></div></div></article></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" id="r-1620336249800" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1620336249800"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1620336249783" data-id="1620336249783"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" id="e-1640635524476" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1640635524476"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><strong>EXCLUSIVE LIMITED EDITION APPAREL IN EVERY BOX</strong></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1686931235127" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-t